## Contract deploy (Hardhat)
# DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY="0xabc... (no quotes needed, but OK)"
# BASE_MAINNET_RPC_URL="https://mainnet.base.org"
# BASE_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL="https://sepolia.base.org"

## Basescan contract verification (https://basescan.org/apis)
# BASESCAN_API_KEY="..."

## Frontend (Next.js)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FORTUNE_COOKIE_ADDRESS="0x..."
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL="https://your-app.vercel.app"
# Optional: Alchemy / Infura / public RPC (defaults to https://mainnet.base.org)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_RPC_URL="https://base-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/..."
# Optional: WalletConnect (https://cloud.walletconnect.com) — enables mobile / QR wallets
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID="..."
